<li><a href="http://www.kalvesmaki.com/LXX/" class="external text" title="http://www.kalvesmaki.com/LXX/" rel="nofollow">The Septuagint Online</a> - Comprehensive site with scholarly discussion and links to texts and translations</li>
<li><a href="http://www.twu.ca/sites/septuagint/" class="external text" title="http://www.twu.ca/sites/septuagint/" rel="nofollow">The Septuagint Institute</a></li>
