<li><a href="http://www.geocities.com/r_grant_jones/Rick/Septuagint/spindex.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.geocities.com/r_grant_jones/Rick/Septuagint/spindex.htm" rel="nofollow">A thorough analysis of the Septuagint with resources</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.exc.com/JoelHoffman/Excerpts/ITB-p95.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.exc.com/JoelHoffman/Excerpts/ITB-p95.pdf" rel="nofollow">Comparison of names in the LXX and Hebrew Bible</a> (<a href="/wiki/PDF" title="PDF" class="mw-redirect">PDF</a>)</li>
