<li><a href="http://ccat.sas.upenn.edu/rs/rak/earlylxx/earlypaplist.html" class="external text" title="http://ccat.sas.upenn.edu/rs/rak/earlylxx/earlypaplist.html" rel="nofollow">Extensive chronological and canonical list of Early Papyri and Manuscripts of the Septuagint</a></li>
